{"tid":2063727,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英政客籲港人洗版爭BNO平權","createTime":"2020-06-14T08:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T08:57:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f4c232b9c15fe6126baf06d912714c376ff47f9","tid":2063727,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200614/YYCEB643QULEMWVF4LLXL44FUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FYYCEB643QULEMWVF4LLXL44FUM%2F&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJrsYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=8dc0b7a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FYYCEB643QULEMWVF4LLXL44FUM%2F&h=632b7efb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200614/YYCEB643QULEMWVF4LLXL44FUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英政客籲港人洗版爭BNO平權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MDYQX7HPZNAR2L5LHXEOGUNSVM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMDYQX7HPZNAR2L5LHXEOGUNSVM.gif&h=694f9def&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民主黨昨與協助起草《香港法案》的英國自由民主黨黨員舉行視像會議，討論BNO平權。許湖洪攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法即將推行，港人紛紛續領英國國民（海外）護照（BNO），並期望英國政府加強對BNO持有人保障。協助起草《香港法案》的英國自由民主黨成員及組織Friends of Hong Kong創辦人Nick Chan認為，英國政府對國安法立場強硬，對爭取《香港法案》有積極作用。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：稱立法如藤條  湯家驊冀中共「波板糖」懷柔<br />\n<br />\n97年前出生無BNO亦受惠<br />\n<br />\n英國自由民主黨議員Alistair Carmichael今年2月向下議院提交BNO平權法案，獲首讀通過。民主黨國際事務委員會昨透過視。。。。。。。。。。。。。到警暴及記者受打壓等，反映英國對港版國安法持強硬反對態度，認為有助爭取法案。<br />\n<br />\nNick指法案除確保BNO持有人獲英國公民權利，亦可能令1997前出生但無。。。。。。。。。。。。。人入境，「只要人生受到威脅就可以申請」。<br />\n<br />\nFriends of Hong Kong成員Larry Ngan指，英政府會參考港人民意，「香港人。。。。。。。。。。。。。。定要Hong Kong Bill」。他笑言「日日都煩住啲國會議員」，會繼續游說工作。法案9月11日將進行二讀。<br />\n<br />\n■記者許湖洪"},{"pid":"259f243e7b7339cfbad4200bd07a9be5e2f23aa8","tid":2063727,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:51:19.000Z","msg":"四方西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6766ec211a87bcf3c0d67a691a1c76705c6e3503","tid":2063727,"uid":45523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:53:42.000Z","msg":"有四方西即刻退後兩步保持距離啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4246a68f7d38eae38866e408c0188c696bf862","tid":2063727,"uid":74935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"}]}